  "source_notes": "Castellanos quotes birth certificate [https://pbs.twimg.com/media/BieWnb4CIAI4y-E.png].\\nSy Scholfield quotes from \"Chepito, the oldest person in Costa Rica, dies at the age 121\" by Rico, ''Q Costa Rica'', 27 May 2021: \"José Uriel Delgado Corrales, known as Chepito, died this Thursday night, confirmed the Home for the Hogar de Ancianos de Piedades de Santa Ana, in San José, where the man lived.... According to the director of the home for the elderly, Sister María Inés, Delgado Corrales died at 8:30 pm.... He was born at 10 pm on March 10, 1900. He was baptized in the San Miguel de Escazú parish on the 12th of the same month and year.\" [https://qcostarica.com/chepito-the-oldest-person-in-costa-rica-dies-at-the-age-121/].\\n\\n",
